#### AI description  (iteration 1)
#### PR Classification
Configuration changes in preparation for introducing kexec.

#### PR Summary
This pull request updates configuration settings to enable kexec-related features.
- `Microsoft/mshv_sk_config`: Enabled `CONFIG_KEXEC_FILE`, `CONFIG_KEXEC_SIG`, `CONFIG_KEXEC_BZIMAGE_VERIFY_SIG`, and `CONFIG_KEXEC_CORE`.
- `kernel/Kconfig.kexec`: Modified dependencies for `KEXEC` and `KEXEC_JUMP` to exclude `HEKI`.
- `Microsoft/lvbs.config`: Enabled `CONFIG_MODULE_SIG_FORCE` and disabled `CONFIG_IMA`.
